    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low until very gently bubbling and cook, covered, for 15 min</p><p>After 15 min, remove the pot from the heat and keep covered for a further 10 min before serving – this is your <strong>sticky rice</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Keep the lid on the whole time to get fluffy and sticky rice!</p>",
