    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> and <strong>sliced radishes</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside for later – this is your <strong>pickled veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
