    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Add<strong> </strong>a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> and the <strong>miso glaze </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 10-12 min, covered, or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
