    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>miso-glazed chicken</strong> <strong>breast</strong> with the <strong>sticky rice</strong> and <strong>pickled veg</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon any <strong>remaining miso glaze </strong>over the chicken</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>black</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
